title: Tomb of the Silent Dragon
story: The tomb of the Silent Dragon is situated at the center of a lake. Recently a band of hobgoblins rediscovered it, making it their center of operation. Rumors say that a legendary stone Korva is still hidden here.

notes.text: A chest with a mysterious, warm to touch tome.
Remains of a human, some gold clutched in his hands.
A rotten sarcophagus holds a seashell-shaped key.
A seashell-shaped key hidden in a crevice of the wall.
A charming monk, lying in a corner.
A lavishly decorated gate with three keyholes on the northern wall of the small chamber.
A stuffed halfling with a seashell-shaped key in their hands.
A rear entrance into the tomb. A tapestry on the wall, totally destroyed by fire.
